{"tid":2125690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO心急人致電英國心儀學校，查詢何時開始收生 校方：WHAT IS BNO???","createTime":"2020-07-26T10:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T11:13:53.000Z","uid":28114,"like":66,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb474dee1162982f3c304739bd69d024f987a10","tid":2125690,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"《你以為你很英國》<br />\n<br />\nBNO心急人託英國朋友致電心儀學校，查詢何時開始收BNO子女學生。<br />\n<br />\n校方回應：WHAT IS BNO???<br />\n<br />\n#英國民間柒苦<br />\n#英國田野吹哨報告<br />\n#吓哦我都係返出去先<br />\n<br />\n圖片與事件中學校無關：<br />\nQueen Elizabeth&rsquo;s Grammar School, Blackburn<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101138131381222/posts/180144416813926/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101138131381222%2Fposts%2F180144416813926%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLiLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=23bfb7ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101138131381222/posts/180144416813926/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"fba821a2cdf107f998934c99ff12019f406a1431","tid":2125690,"uid":28114,"like":81,"dislike":16,"score":65,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T10:43:15.000Z","msg":"港燦又衝出嚟丟人現眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f527f6b82022495a24770c3329cdab74f52e06fc","tid":2125690,"uid":279938,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"其實講話黎緊會有resident visa會唔會容易明白啲呢？<br />\n<br />\n畢竟個小朋友係乜國籍對學校嚟講唔太relevant"},{"pid":"21506dd16700da5f2d6fb9724fc6f79d500ee246","tid":2125690,"uid":38904,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"正如你都唔會知身份證得1粒星2粒星嘅人揸乜嘢護照"},{"pid":"20121fbae3bbb46e072925f8422e8b180f392509","tid":2125690,"uid":28114,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"quote":{"pid":"f527f6b82022495a24770c3329cdab74f52e06fc","tid":2125690,"uid":279938,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"其實講話黎緊會有resident visa